      "rationale": "Testing was conducted under a single standardized ASTM F1717 load condition (quasi-static, 5 mm/min crosshead speed, room temperature). Only one test condition was evaluated; variation in loading rate or environment was not explored. This limits the achieved level to 2, which is below the required level of 3. This known gap is acknowledged in the overall credibility assessment."
